    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Blueprint-callable factory for constructing concrete node params objects.</para>
<para>Allows Blueprints to create typed params for ChangeParams() and graph authoring without any per-project C++ glue.</para>
<para>Usage (Blueprint): MakeGenerateParams → set fields → Agent.ChangeParams(NodeName, Params) CloneParams(Baseline) → set one field → Agent.ChangeParams(NodeName, Cloned) </para>
    </detaileddescription>
